OL,3,CHealth trusts outline 'catastrophic'
OL,4,Cimpact of financial pressures
OL,6,FThe heads of Northern Ireland's health
OL,7,Ftrusts have joined forces to warn of
OL,8,Fthe "catastrophic impacts" which
OL,9,Ffinancial pressures .
OL,11,FIn an unprecedented public
OL,12,Fintervention, they said there could be
OL,13,Fbed closures, cuts to operating lists
OL,14,Fand reduced domiciliary care if
OL,15,Fadditional funding is not found.
