OL,3,CHealth trusts outline 'catastrophic'
OL,4,Cimpact of financial pressures
OL,6,FWithout further funding this year, the
OL,7,Fchairs flagged the potential for a
OL,8,Frange of sweeping cutbacks, including
OL,9,Fbed closures and reductions in
OL,10,Foutpatient care provision, operating
OL,11,Flists, and domiciliary care and
OL,12,Fnursing care packages.
OL,14,FNew Health Minister, Mike Nesbitt,
OL,15,Fsaid he has been left stunned by
OL,16,Fbriefings he has received on the
OL,17,Fbudget situation facing health
OL,18,Fservices.
