OL,6,FIn his introductory statement as
OL,7,Fminister at Stormont on Monday, he
OL,8,Fsaid: "I do not want a two-tier health
OL,9,Fservice where timely access to
OL,10,Ftreatments is the preserve of those
OL,11,Fwho can afford to go private.
OL,13,F"I do not want to live in a society
OL,14,Fwhere those who live in deprived areas
OL,15,Fhave such pronounced lower life
OL,16,Fexpectancy, have greater health
OL,17,Fstruggles and worse outcomes.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
