OL,6,F"That, of course, is a challenge for
OL,7,Fall parts of government. I want to
OL,8,Fwork with my ministerial colleagues
OL,9,Fand the resources I have to develop
OL,10,Fhow we could do more to address health
OL,11,Finequalties at a community level and
OL,12,Fwill bring back more detailed plans in
OL,13,Fdue course."
OL,15,FLast week the Stormont Assembly backed
OL,16,Fa budget in a vote that saw then-
OL,17,Fhealth minister Robin Swann and his
OL,18,FUlster Unionist colleagues oppose the
OL,19,Fspending plan.
