OL,3,CHealth trusts outline 'catastrophic'
OL,4,Cimpact of financial pressures
OL,6,FMr Nesbitt has since replaced his
OL,7,Fparty colleague.
OL,9,FHe repeated to MLAs his determination
OL,10,Fthat he would not implement cuts which
OL,11,Fwould lead to "catastrophic impacts"
OL,12,Fon health services in the region.
OL,14,FSetting out the implications of trying
OL,15,Fto make savings within his department,
OL,16,FMr Nesbitt said this would involve
OL,17,Fmaking decisions that will "not be
OL,18,Fwithout significant controversy".
