OL,3,CHealth trusts outline 'catastrophic'
OL,4,Cimpact of financial pressures
OL,6,FIn their joint statement, the six
OL,7,Ftrust chairs said they were "deeply
OL,8,Fconcerned at the financial outlook for
OL,9,Fthe frontline services which our
OL,10,Forganisations deliver".
OL,12,F"We have no wish to be involved in
OL,13,Fpolitical controversy and are very
OL,14,Fmindful of the growing budgetary
OL,15,Fpressures on all parts of the public
OL,16,Fsector," they added.
OL,18,F"Our focus has to be on everyone in
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland who needs the health
OL,20,Fand social care services that our
OL,21,Forganisations provide.
OL,26,@oD@]OUrD@VO]tD@AOUxD@HO]zD@AOU
