OL,3,CHealth trusts outline 'catastrophic'
OL,4,Cimpact of financial pressures
OL,6,F"It is our duty to warn of the very
OL,7,Freal potential for avoidable and
OL,8,Fserious harm being caused to people in
OL,9,Four community who require our help, as
OL,10,Fa result of inadequate budgetary
OL,11,Fprovision.
OL,13,F"HSC Trusts have, of course, an
OL,14,Fonerous responsibility to make
OL,15,Fefficient use of all public resources.
OL,16,FIntensive efforts are ongoing to
OL,17,Fdeliver a significant level of savings
OL,18,Fthis year, as detailed in the
OL,19,Ffinancial assessment published on 28/
OL,20,F05/2024 by the Department of Health.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G7/12
