PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F449A1717561531
OL,3,CHealth trusts outline 'catastrophic'
OL,4,Cimpact of financial pressures
OL,6,F"As this document makes clear, even
OL,7,Fwith these savings, a projected very
OL,8,Fsignificant shortfall remains that
OL,9,Fcould only be filled by measures with
OL,10,Fhigh and catastrophic impacts.
OL,12,F"Such cutbacks would inevitably
OL,13,Finclude bed closures as well as
OL,14,Freductions in outpatient care,
OL,15,Foperating lists, domiciliary care and
OL,16,Fnursing care packages.
OL,18,F"This would impact damagingly on the
OL,19,Fwhole community in Northern Ireland,
OL,20,Fparticularly the most vulnerable.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
