OL,3,CHealth trusts outline 'catastrophic'
OL,4,Cimpact of financial pressures
OL,6,F"We are keenly aware of the need to
OL,7,Freform services and invest in new
OL,8,Ftechnology. We know too that health
OL,9,Fdrives our economy and contributes on
OL,10,Fnumerous levels to well-being in
OL,11,Fsociety.
OL,13,F"The reality is that without
OL,14,Fsignificant additional funding this
OL,15,Fyear and longer-term financial
OL,16,Fsecurity, the Health Service will be
OL,17,Ffurther destabilised and the public
OL,18,Fwill bear the brunt.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
