OL,6,F"We have a collective responsibility
OL,7,Fas leaders to highlight these
OL,8,Fconcerns, on behalf of our dedicated
OL,9,Fworkforce and all those who rely on
OL,10,Fthe vital services our organisations
OL,11,Fprovide.
OL,13,F"We will continue to work
OL,14,Fconstructively with staff, elected
OL,15,Frepresentatives and other stakeholders
OL,16,Fto pursue the best outcomes for
OL,17,Fpatients and service users.
