OL,6,F"Health and social care services have
OL,7,Fendured a prolonged period of
OL,8,Finstability and pressure. The
OL,9,Fescalating budgetary situation
OL,10,Frepresents another destabilising
OL,11,Ffactor."
OL,13,FThe statement was issued by South
OL,14,FEastern Trust chair Jonathan Patton,
OL,15,FNorthern Trust chair Anne O'Reilly,
OL,16,FBelfast Trust chair Ciaran Mulgrew,
OL,17,FSouthern Trust chair Eileen Mullan,
OL,18,FWestern Trust chair Tom Frawley and
OL,19,Fchair of the Ambulance Service Michele
OL,20,FLarmour.
